WEBVTT

00:00.022 --> 00:01.421
I want your body
one last time

00:01.457 --> 00:03.023
<i>before I walk down that aisle.</i>

00:03.058 --> 00:04.691
Sheila's getting married,

00:04.727 --> 00:06.727
and she wants to have
one last fling.

00:06.762 --> 00:07.828
Whatever you decide,

00:07.863 --> 00:10.030
it's not going to change
how I feel about you.

00:10.065 --> 00:11.109
You knew I was
seeing someone,

00:11.133 --> 00:12.766
and you did that to me anyway.

00:12.801 --> 00:14.112
If it didn't affect you,
then just go ahead

00:14.136 --> 00:15.536
and tell her you
didn't do anything.

00:15.571 --> 00:16.537
Don't you get it?

00:16.572 --> 00:17.572
You made me the one thing

00:17.606 --> 00:18.939
I never wanted to be.

00:18.974 --> 00:20.741
It was a kiss, Harvey!

00:20.776 --> 00:22.509
We've done more than that.

00:22.545 --> 00:24.523
Unless, of course, you haven't
told her that, either?

00:24.547 --> 00:26.680
The other night, when you
said that you were surprised

00:26.715 --> 00:29.883
that nothing had ever happened
between me and Donna before,

00:29.919 --> 00:31.552
I should've said something.

00:31.587 --> 00:33.787
It was years ago,
and it was only one time,

00:33.822 --> 00:35.856
but Donna and I slept together.

00:35.891 --> 00:39.459
Say something.

00:45.401 --> 00:47.434
<i>Say something, please, Paula.
- Okay.</i>

00:47.469 --> 00:48.613
You want me to say something?

00:48.637 --> 00:49.603
This is the second time

00:49.638 --> 00:51.705
that you haven't told me
the full truth

00:51.740 --> 00:53.574
in as many conversations.

00:53.609 --> 00:54.975
That's not fair,
and you know it.

00:55.010 --> 00:56.655
No, you are not the one
who should be deciding

00:56.679 --> 00:58.712
what is fair
and what's not fair right now.

00:58.747 --> 01:00.447
<i>What's that supposed
to mean?</i>

01:00.482 --> 01:01.626
<i>It means that you want me</i>
<i>to yell at you</i>

01:01.650 --> 01:02.449
<i>so that you can get past this.</i>

01:02.484 --> 01:04.483
<i>Well, I'm not past it,</i>

01:04.519 --> 01:05.964
<i>and right now, what I need</i>
<i>is some time to myself.</i>

01:05.988 --> 01:06.720
Paula, please.

01:06.755 --> 01:07.988
No.
If you can't put

01:08.023 --> 01:09.089
my need to process

01:09.124 --> 01:10.223
over your need to feel okay

01:10.259 --> 01:11.725
about yourself...

01:11.760 --> 01:14.061
then I'm afraid
we'll never get past this.

01:15.598 --> 01:16.608
<i>What's the matter with you?</i>

01:16.632 --> 01:17.598
Put your goddamn weight

01:17.633 --> 01:18.599
into the punches.

01:18.634 --> 01:19.566
Let's go.

01:23.439 --> 01:24.679
I said hit me like you mean it.

