01:36.018 --> 01:37.584
That good enough for you?

01:49.131 --> 01:52.099
<i>Louis,</i>
<i>this is your safe place.</i>

01:52.134 --> 01:53.767
<i>You feel dirty,</i>

01:53.802 --> 01:56.470
<i>but soon,</i>
<i>your mind and your body</i>

01:56.505 --> 01:59.773
<i>will be as pure as snow.</i>

01:59.808 --> 02:02.542
<i>Let the mud</i>
<i>wash away your troubles</i>

02:02.578 --> 02:04.211
<i>as it enters your pores.</i>

02:04.246 --> 02:06.446
<i>It is not an intrusion.</i>

02:06.482 --> 02:08.882
<i>It is a cleansing,</i>
<i>wonderful--</i>

02:08.917 --> 02:10.116
God damn it, Ricardo.

02:10.151 --> 02:12.152
I told you to not
interrupt me--

02:12.187 --> 02:14.488
Sheila.

02:14.523 --> 02:15.800
What are you doing here?
- Louis,

02:15.824 --> 02:16.723
ever since the other night,

02:16.759 --> 02:17.524
I've been wrestling
with whether

02:17.559 --> 02:18.992
I made the right decision.

02:19.028 --> 02:20.160
So have I,

02:20.195 --> 02:20.961
but I don't--
I don't think that--

02:20.996 --> 02:22.162
Then we're in agreement,

02:22.197 --> 02:23.630
which means we can do it

02:23.666 --> 02:27.200
again and again

02:27.236 --> 02:30.470
and again--Ah!
- Oh, mommy.

02:30.506 --> 02:31.972
And again.

02:32.007 --> 02:33.206
And Ag--
- Wait a second.

02:33.242 --> 02:34.519
Wait a second, wait a second,
Sheila.

02:34.543 --> 02:35.876
I need to know.
Does this mean

02:35.911 --> 02:37.678
you're not marrying
your fiancé?

02:37.713 --> 02:38.812
No, it doesn't.

02:38.847 --> 02:39.813
The wedding's next week.

02:39.848 --> 02:43.650
Sheila, listen to me.

02:43.686 --> 02:45.252
That night

02:45.287 --> 02:47.654
was one of the greatest nights
of my entire life,

02:47.690 --> 02:50.424
but the next morning
was one of the worst.

02:50.459 --> 02:52.726
I can't do this.

02:52.761 --> 02:55.028
I just--I can't.

02:55.064 --> 02:57.164
Louis,

02:57.199 --> 03:00.667
I know you better
than you know yourself,

03:00.703 --> 03:02.602
and I know it's only
a matter of time

03:02.638 --> 03:05.072
before you change your mind.

03:05.107 --> 03:08.709
So I'm going to give you
a couple of days,

03:08.744 --> 03:09.854
and then I'm going
to contact you

03:09.878 --> 03:11.845
on this.

03:11.880 --> 03:13.113
It's a burner phone,

03:13.148 --> 03:15.582
and it's <i> completely</i>
untraceable,

03:15.617 --> 03:17.584
so when I call,

03:17.619 --> 03:18.752
you better be ready.
- Yeah?

03:18.787 --> 03:20.854
And when I say "ready,"

03:20.889 --> 03:22.889
what I mean is...

03:22.925 --> 03:26.526
No, no, no, no, no...

03:26.562 --> 03:28.895
Chubby Checker.

03:30.065 --> 03:31.932
Atta boy.

03:38.841 --> 03:40.240
Shit.
That's twice now.

03:46.348 --> 03:49.082
- Jessica.
<i>- Good morning, Harvey.</i>

03:49.118 --> 03:50.717
I take it you saw
the press release.

03:50.753 --> 03:52.753
<i>I did.</i>

03:52.788 --> 03:54.888
I'm sorry that it had to be
that harsh.

03:54.923 --> 03:56.890
<i>It's okay, Harvey.</i>

03:56.925 --> 03:58.069
<i>We both know</i>
<i>it was the only way</i>

03:58.093 --> 03:59.137
<i>I was going to get my money</i>

03:59.161 --> 04:00.727
<i>and let you keep the firm.</i>

04:00.763 --> 04:02.229
<i>But now,</i>
<i>I need something from you.</i>

04:02.264 --> 04:03.797
- Anything.
<i>- I need</i>

04:03.832 --> 04:05.766
$2 million of that money

04:05.801 --> 04:08.969
in an untraceable account.

04:09.004 --> 04:11.304
Jessica, the threshold
for putting money like that

04:11.340 --> 04:13.073
into an account is $10,000.

04:13.108 --> 04:14.574
<i>I'm not keen</i>
<i>on making this happen</i>

04:14.610 --> 04:15.776
<i>without knowing why.</i>

04:15.811 --> 04:17.144
Well, I'm not
telling you why,

04:17.178 --> 04:18.745
but what you're really asking

04:18.781 --> 04:20.346
is am I trying
to break the law?

04:20.382 --> 04:22.883
<i>- Are you?</i>
- No.

04:22.918 --> 04:24.262
I'll declare it
when I'm finished with it.

04:24.286 --> 04:25.819
You have my word on that.

04:25.854 --> 04:27.621
Well, if we get caught
doing this

04:27.656 --> 04:29.589
before you declare it,
it is breaking the law,

04:29.625 --> 04:32.092
so why can't you tell me
what it's for?

04:32.127 --> 04:33.627
<i>Because you don't need</i>
<i>to know,</i>

04:33.662 --> 04:34.594
and I shouldn't have to

04:34.630 --> 04:36.062
tell you what it's for,

04:36.098 --> 04:37.275
because the reason
you're getting me

04:37.299 --> 04:38.598
that money in the first place

04:38.634 --> 04:40.333
is that I saved your ass
not once,

04:40.369 --> 04:41.835
<i>but twice,</i>

04:41.870 --> 04:42.947
<i>so you're either</i>
<i>gonna do this</i>

04:42.971 --> 04:44.271
or you're not.

04:44.306 --> 04:45.939
Which is it?

04:48.710 --> 04:49.879
I'll get it done.

